data.description: Step into this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom starter home where modern convenience meets comfort. The house features stylish and low-maintenance tile flooring, providing a seamless flow throughout. A recent kitchen remodel introduces a contemporary touch with updated appliances, sleek cabinetry, and a spacious layout that connects seamlessly to the dining area. A highlight of this home is the new A/C and furnace, ensuring year-round comfort. The master bedroom boasts a tranquil retreat with an ensuite bedroom, while three additional bedrooms are versatile for guests or a home office. Step outside to a backyard with potential for outdoor activities and relaxation. This turnkey home is perfect for those seeking a blend of functionality and style in a 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven. Enjoy the perks of recent renovations and make lasting memeories in this living space.
